language ESSENCE' 1.0

given indexSize: int
find m: matrix indexed by [int(1..indexSize), int(1..indexSize)] of bool
such that
    and([sum([!m[r, c] | c : int(1..indexSize)]) = 11 | r : int(1..indexSize)]),
    and([sum([!m[r, c] | r : int(1..indexSize)]) = 11 | c : int(1..indexSize)]),
    and([sum([!(m[r1, c] \/ m[r2, c]) | c : int(1..indexSize)]) = 1
             | r1 : int(1..indexSize), r2 : int(1..indexSize), r1 != r2])

